54
00:05:27.035 --> 00:05:27.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Señor.

55
00:05:28.786 --> 00:05:31.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He limpiado la zona
para que haya un mejor ambiente.

56
00:05:32.373 --> 00:05:34.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He traído mi propia máquina.

57
00:05:35.043 --> 00:05:36.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Tiene papel?

58
00:05:36.753 --> 00:05:39.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No. Lo venden en la tienda del puerto.

59
00:05:40.214 --> 00:05:41.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ve a comprarlo.

60
00:05:42.050 --> 00:05:45.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Y ya de paso, compra la cena.
Quiero pasta a la carbonara.

61
00:05:46.804 --> 00:05:47.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Señor.

62
00:05:48.181 --> 00:05:50.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Soy escribiente, no criada.

63
00:05:53.978 --> 00:05:55.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Es usted difícil.

64
00:05:58.316 --> 00:06:00.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Tengo todos los ingredientes que necesita.</i>

65
00:06:01.027 --> 00:06:02.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Muchas gracias.

66
