68
00:06:11.412 --> 00:06:14.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rompes el huevo y separas la yema.

69
00:06:15.291 --> 00:06:16.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿La yema?

70
00:06:25.468 --> 00:06:26.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Qué haces?

71
00:06:27.553 --> 00:06:29.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Intento cocinar.

72
00:06:40.024 --> 00:06:43.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No está mal para ser la primera vez.

73
00:06:44.779 --> 00:06:48.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
