- Comeré más tarde.

74
00:06:48.616 --> 00:06:49.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Entiendo.

75
00:07:09.178 --> 00:07:10.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
