81
00:07:31.659 --> 00:07:33.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ahora habla Olive.

82
00:07:34.537 --> 00:07:36.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Debemos cruzar este valle de fuego

83
00:07:37.415 --> 00:07:39.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
