97
00:08:18.122 --> 00:08:19.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Sí?

98
00:08:19.916 --> 00:08:21.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Me parece estar viviendo esa experiencia,

99
00:08:22.543 --> 00:08:24.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
