100
00:08:26.214 --> 00:08:29.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Me siento como esa chica, Olive.

101
00:08:30.259 --> 00:08:32.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
