102
00:08:32.970 --> 00:08:34.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No estoy segura.

103
00:08:35.097 --> 00:08:36.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Por qué?

104
00:08:38.226 --> 00:08:45.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
