110
00:09:07.046 --> 00:09:12.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sí, pero al hacerlo, pierde su capacidad
para hablar con los espíritus.

111
00:09:13.386 --> 00:09:14.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No.

112
00:09:14.637 --> 00:09:16.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Entonces, ¿cómo volverá a casa?

113
00:09:17.515 --> 00:09:19.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
