115
00:09:23.521 --> 00:09:24.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Pues debería.

116
00:09:26.023 --> 00:09:26.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
