la está esperando.

118
00:09:33.447 --> 00:09:34.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Se le ha ocurrido algo?

119
00:09:40.913 --> 00:09:42.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hoy hace buen tiempo.

120
00:09:43.499 --> 00:09:45.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, demasiado bueno.

121
00:09:47.044 --> 00:09:47.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Señor.

122
00:09:51.549 --> 00:09:52.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Qué es esto?

123
00:09:53.134 --> 00:09:55.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
