125
00:09:58.347 --> 00:10:00.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Es una sombrilla preciosa.

126
00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:07.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Necesito...

127
00:10:08.357 --> 00:10:09.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
...un descanso.

128
00:10:25.249 --> 00:10:26.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
