135
00:10:44.518 --> 00:10:45.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Vete a casa.

136
00:10:48.272 --> 00:10:50.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Entonces no terminará la obra.

137
00:10:51.442 --> 00:10:53.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
